 Install Font Awesome (Optional)
To get the Twitter icon and quote icons working, you can either:

Option A: Use CDN (already included in App.css)

css
/* Already added in App.css */
@import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');
Option B: Install via npm

bash
npm install @fortawesome/fontawesome-free
Then add to src/index.js:

javascript
import '@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/css/all.min.css';
9. Install and Run
bash
# Create React App if you haven't already
npx create-react-app quote-generator
cd quote-generator

# Create the files as described above
# Then start the application
npm start